                "content": "作为一个在加拿大生活多年的华人，MOECA让我感到久违的文化归属感。这里不只是博物馆，更是心灵的故乡。",
                "author": "王建国",
                "location": "渥太华，加拿大"
            },
            {
                "content": "The ink tiger paintings by Zhang Jinsheng are unlike anything I have seen before. Raw power and ancient tradition meet in a way that is truly unforgettable.",
